4
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:40,800
♪ Fate changes and cannot be predicted  ♪

5
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:44,250
♪ Ask the road and journey ahead ♪

6
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:47,580
♪ Where is my soul mate? ♪

7
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:50,580
