20
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:35,970
♪ I’ve forgotten those who are gone ♪

21
00:01:45,130 --> 00:01:49,910
[Word of Honor]

22
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:53,080
[Episode 32]

23
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,080
[Sanjun Mansion]

24
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,999
Looking back, I was drinking
joyfully with my friends

25
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:59,239
but now everything has changed.

26
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:02,559
The things in front of me
are still the same as before,

27
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:05,119
but the ones doing it are different.

28
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,479
Everything in the world changes,
so do the relationship between people.

29
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:10,639
Zi Shu, come on and have a drink.

30
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,119
Good idea.

31
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,679
Ping An, give me a bowl of wine.

32
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,239
Sick Dude, stop thinking of it.

33
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,879
Master asked me to take care of you

34
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,639
before he left.

35
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,719
Just a little. It doesn’t matter.

36
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,679
No.

37
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,119
Not even a drop.

38
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,479
Wu Xi,

39
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,119
you’re giving me a hard time.

40
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,679
You know only wine
can give me happiness.

41
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:33,999
Leader Zhou,

42
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,119
you’re the one who’s giving me a hard time.

43
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,320
Your injuries are so rare and odd

44
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:41,400
that even if your body
is already in the best condition,

45
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,880
I’m not completely sure I can cure you.

46
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:44,880
So stop thinking of it.

47
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,799
You must not drink

48
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,999
or fool around

49
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,119
until you’re healed.

50
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,799
Wu Xi.

51
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:56,039
You’re cute when you talk seriously.

52
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,039
You don’t have to be completely sure,

53
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,439
only half as sure.

54
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,559
As a man, I should drink as much as I want.

55
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,119
If you don’t listen to the advice,

56
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,679
I’ll tell Master when he comes back.

57
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,839
Fine, fine.

58
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,639
I will also tell him that

59
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,599
a tricky maid gave me a hard time.

60
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,079
Leader Zhou.

61
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,559
You’ve long lost the sense of smell and taste,

62
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,959
drinking or not makes no difference to you.

63
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,079
Drink the tea.

64
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,679
But...

65
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,399
Let’s have a drink.

66
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:23,839
Come on.

67
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:25,750
Cheers.

68
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,279
It’s not the wine I’m seeking,

69
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,119
but a feeling.

70
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,919
Zi Shu.

71
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:34,119
Looks like we can;t drink together this time.

72
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,639
I remember once we agreed that

73
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,999
if we can still meet each other,
we must drink until we’re wasted.

74
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:42,279
All these years I have waited long
in South Xinjiang,

75
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:45,199
but someone has never come.

76
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,479
I still remember someone asked me

77
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,879
to hep him find a girl

78
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,639
with a great shape.

79
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,399
I found alot,

80
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,119
but he...

81
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,599
Come on, cheers.

82
00:03:58,880 --> 00:03:59,679
Cheers.

83
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,839
We’ll make sure you have a good time!

84
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,479
Ah Xiang.

85
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:04,759
Lord Seven.

86
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,999
Qin Lai.

87
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,919
Didn’t I ask you to stay with Cheng Ling?

88
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,999
Why did you come back first?

89
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,399
Where’s Cheng Ling?

90
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,919
Young Master Cheng Ling is fine.

91
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,279
but he won’t let me serve him anymore.

92
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,159
What’s wrong?

93
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,399
I don’t know either.

94
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,119
Leader Shen asked Cheng Ling

95
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:22,399
if he knew that Master Wen Ke Xing

96
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,679
is the Chief of Ghost Valley.

97
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,159
He got extremely furious and cried alot,

98
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:28,319
and then let me come back.

99
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,359
<i>Now that Cheng Ling knows the identity of Lao Wen</i>

100
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,119
<i>at this point,</i>

101
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:35,359
<i>I need to discuss with Lao Wen.</i>

102
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,279
Leader Zhou.

103
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,119
This is the elixir I made for you

104
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,119
with all the power I pooled in South Xinjiang
to maintain your life.

105
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:42,879
No, thanks.

106
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,319
I’m going to solve

107
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,999
the misunderstanding between Lao Wen
and Cheng Ling.

108
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,679
Lao Wen promised me that

109
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,439
he will no longer manage the Ghost Valley.

110
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,679
He is back to pick up one thing,

111
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,159
and then he’ll live a cloistered live with me.

112
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:56,119
Just in case, please keep it.

113
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,999
No matter how badly injured one is,

114
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,919
the elixir can help him recover half his life.

115
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,919
What if Master Wen needs it?

116
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,719
Don’t curse him.

117
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,199
Just take it.

118
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,879
Here’s your dish, sir.

119
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,959
With the white deer pastured
in the verdant cliffs,

120
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,999
I can always ride it to appreciate noted mounts*.
(*Lit: <i>A Visit to Mount Tainmu</i> by Li Bai)

121
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,999
It is said that the Ghost Valley is gloomy,

122
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:45,199
but I feel that the Mount Qingya
is quite peaceful.

123
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,719
Why are you guys still here?

124
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,639
Hurry up, or you will miss it.

125
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,839
Brother, what happened?

126
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,759
Haven’t you heard about it?

127
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,439
Chief of the Ghost Valley is caught in a siege

128
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,039
and chased by the Five Lakes Alliance
to the White Deer Cliff.

129
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,279
He will die soon.

130
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,279
If he dies,

131
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,839
the demons will dissipate.

132
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,359
Come with me if you want to see something fun,

133
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,159
or there will be filled with crowds.

134
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,439
I’m leaving now.

135
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,039
Let’s go.

136
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:00,079
Brother Wen, stop struggling.

137
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:03,039
Just surrender.

138
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,159
If you listen to my words,

139
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,999
I promise that you won’t be torn apart.

140
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,679
What if I say no?

141
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,999
How dare you!

142
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,639
Even if your martial arts skills are excellent,

143
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,879
can you compete with so many of our masters?

144
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,079
We don’t have to

145
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,239
follow any code with him.

146
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,599
Let’s rush together

147
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,039
to kill him!

148
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:25,439
Kill him! Kill him!

149
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:28,239
As I said before, I’ll kill anyone
who comes near me.

150
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,239
It’s true that I can’t kill all of you.

151
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,959
It just depends on which one of you wants to die,

152
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,039
or to live.

153
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,519
Everyone, see?

154
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,759
This is the key to the World’s Armory that you want.

155
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,519
You can open the World’s Armory

156
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,119
with this key,

157
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,839
instead of the Glazed Armor.

158
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,919
Do you want it?

159
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,879
Kill me,

160
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,639
and it would be yours.

161
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,279
Great. Kill him now.

162
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,279
Don’t be fooled by him.

163
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,919
We can kill the Valley Chief,

164
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,799
and share the World’s Armory together.

165
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,039
Well, Scorpion,

166
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,679
I’ve undergone ups and downs all this life,

167
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,599
but I never thought

168
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,479
I’d fall under the treacherous plan
of you bastard!

169
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,199
Chief Wen, all is fair in war.

170
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,999
You can cheat others,

171
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,999
but you won’t allow them to cheat you?

172
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,359
Scorpion, you don’t need to talk too much.

173
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:33,919
Brother Wen, did you hear that?

174
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:37,199
It’s not me who wants to kill you,

175
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,359
but God.

176
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,879
I only regret that I was soft-hearted

177
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,999
and didn’t kill you to avenge my father.

178
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,279
Zhen Ru Yu lived an honorable and clean life,

179
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,119
but he has a devilish son like you!

180
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,359
If they could know this,

181
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,399
they must be ashamed of you.

182
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,399
As one of his brothers,

183
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:58,519
it’s my duty to kill you today.

184
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:01,279
I will erase the shame for Brother Zhen.

185
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,719
Cheng Ling, I...

186
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,759
Stop!

187
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:07,079
I’ll never forgive you for destroying my family!

188
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,879
Cheng Ling!

189
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:14,839
Fine.

190
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,439
I...

191
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,519
I shouldn’t have destroyed the Zhang family.

192
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:23,479
Zhang Yu Sen did nothing wrong to my father.

193
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,759
Cheng Ling.

194
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,799
Kill me to avenge your family!

195
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,479
I’m tired.

196
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,879
I won’t fight back

197
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,679
if you kill me.

198
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,799
Let me go!

199
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,839
Cheng Ling, you can’t go.

200
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,359
You can’t trust a devil’s words.

201
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,239
He’s going to die today no matter what.

202
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,519
I can’t let you go.

203
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,039
I won’t lie to you.

204
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,599
Cheng Ling, kill me

205
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,119
and I won’t fight back.

206
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,239
You liar!

207
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,399
All of your words are lies.

208
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:56,439
Wen Ke Xing, you deceived my master for so long!

209
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,879
I, I...

210
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,879
He didn’t lie to me.

211
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,999
Cheng Ling, do you believe in me?

212
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,559
Zhou Zi Shu.

213
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,199
Stop deluding Cheng Ling.

214
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,839
Brother Qin was such a righteous man.

215
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,519
How can he have such a wicked disciple like you?

216
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:28,759
Zhou Zi Shu,

217
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,639
I cheated all of you.

218
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,159
Good and evil can never exist together.

219
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,999
As the Chief of the Ghost Valley,

220
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,599
I’m baleful for this world.

221
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,679
Stop it.

222
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,399
Leader Zhou, you belong to a famous sect,

223
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,879
and your master and I were old friends.

224
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,359
It’s not too late for you

225
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,919
to stand on the right side.

226
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:28,359
Wen Ke Xing must die today!

227
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,479
This bastard is very cunning

228
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,759
and even cheated me.

229
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,359
Don’t fall for his tricks.

230
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,919
Stop your nonsense.

231
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,719
Do you want to fight one by one,

232
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,239
or attack together?

233
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:42,439
Shame on you.

234
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,959
A couple of vicious demons!

235
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,079
Kill them both!

236
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,319
Kill them! Kill them!

237
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,239
Bastard.

238
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,799
Wen Ke Xing, I once said

239
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,279
that I will kill you

240
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,199
when I see you again in the martial arts world.

241
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,279
Alright.

242
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,359
Come and have a try.

243
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,239
Who is this man in white?

244
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:45,359
He is the Changming Sword Immortal,

245
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,359
the master of Rong Xuan.

246
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,879
It’s said that he is the only person in the world

247
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:51,479
who has completely mastered
the Combined Six Cultivation Method.

248
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,279
He has completely masted it to a poised level.

249
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,719
I didn’t expect
the Combined Six Cultivation Method

250
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,799
can be so powerful.

251
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,439
Senior Ye, watch out!

252
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:34,559
Let me help you.

253
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:35,519
Cheng Ling.

254
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,239
Cheng Ling!

255
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,479
It’s dangerous!
Don’t get closer, Cheng Ling.

256
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,279
Get out of here.

257
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,279
Lao Wen!

258
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:32,479
Lao Wen!

259
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,319
<i>Why?</i>

260
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:46,519
Master!

261
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,279
Cheng Ling!

262
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,119
Master!

263
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:58,400
♪ The more I expected
the more unpredictable it was ♪

264
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:01,920
♪ Twined by the carnal thoughts ♪

265
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:08,720
♪ The rain washed my love and hatred ♪

266
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:12,400
♪ It bloomed and swayed ♪

267
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:18,880
♪ I suffered alone and acted calmly ♪

268
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:23,640
♪ Times passed ♪

269
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:29,240
♪ I couldn’t hold onto it,
I couldn’t escape ♪

270
